'''紅腹偽龜'''（[[英語|英語]]：'''northern red-bellied turtle'''，[[學名|學名]]：'''''Pseudemys rubriventris'''''<ref name="Rhodin102"/>）是[[偽龜屬|偽龜屬]]下的一種[[龜|龜]]，原産於[[美國|美國]]。

==描述==

這一種較大的淡水龜，平均長{{convert|29|-|30|cm|in}}，重{{convert|3|kg|lb}}，雌性個體可以長到{{convert|40|cm|in}}長。<ref>[http://www.iucnredlist.org/apps/redlist/details/18460/0 The IUCN Red list of Threatened Species]Pseudemys rubriventris (American Red-bellied Turtle, Northern Red-bellied Cooter, Northern Redbelly Turtle)</ref>

==保護==
[[File:Turtle_from_Pomp's_Pond_in_Andover.jpg|thumb]][[安多弗_(馬薩諸賽州)|安多弗]]的紅腹偽龜]]

在[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]紅腹偽龜是一個受威脅物種，<ref>[http://www.pacode.com/secure/data/058/chapter75/s75.2.html  Threatened species - Pennsylvania]</ref> 被[[美國魚類及野生動物管理局|美國魚類及野生動物管理局]]及麻薩諸塞州分局列為“瀕臨滅絕”。<ref>[http://www.mass.gov/dfwele/dfw/wildlife/facts/reptiles/herp_list.htm http://www.mass.gov/dfwele/dfw/wildlife/facts/reptiles/herp_list.htm] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013075000/http://www.mass.gov/dfwele/dfw/wildlife/facts/reptiles/herp_list.htm |date=2012-10-13 }}</ref>

